reviewText: It was indeed an excellent screensave for your flatscreen in your business, it keeps it ambient, and calm, with no rude humor or anything offensive, cant think of a better way to provide a calm atmosphere to your business

Everything on this DVD is totally FAKE.  My favorite is the graphically inserted, slowly moving sailboat in the background of an ocean view.  At least it got me laughing for a moment. Then I threw it in a garbage.  That's that.
